1. Load the workbook.
2. Locate the INPUT sheet (case‑insensitive) and the OUTPUT sheet (look for a sheet named 'OUTPUT' case‑insensitively; if not found, use the existing 'OUPUT' sheet or create a new one named 'OUTPUT').
